{
  "stem": "15732.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The prime minister, the main ruler of Romania at that time, was a little fellow, was that small, fat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Called [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mironescu. ?] He was, afterwards, I think he-- what-- accused and he was sentenced to death when the Russians came back.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he arrived there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had the luck that one of the soldiers that was my-- that was supposed to guard me-- not guard me-- that I shouldn't escape-- was most probably a nice fellow.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I talked very good Romanian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I explained to him that I have to do something, because I'm unjustifiably there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We are-- that is a big-- we are not Romanian citizens and they [? don't ?] have the right to take us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, he was-- he was good in that respect.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I started going with him and trying to organize-- there were-- I saw quite a few people that were the-- in the same state, [INAUDIBLE] they had this passport.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I organized-- I was a little ball of energy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1941?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was 15 and 1/2. 15 and 1/2.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Organize that we should be in group together, that not each and every one should have to fight for himself.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when those-- we were already several families, one of the-- one of the men saw somebody passing-- a non-Jew, certainly.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he gave him money, he should go immediately into town to alert that particular lawyer that was the [? organizer. ?] After one or two hours, he came.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In the meantime, we saw--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The lawyer arrived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he later had a talk with [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mironescu, ?] who was the-- the super, super chief.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he got an absolvence, at that time, that we can go home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was miracle of miracles.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
